Regulation Name(s): Calculator/data processing module, for clinical use
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Various home-use blood glucose monitors by Roche Diagnostics, Bayer, BD, Johnson & Johnson, Abbott, Nova Biomedical
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for MCT-Diabetes Internet-based software for managing and analyzing blood glucose data from personal glucose monitors
Indications for Use Summary: Serves as an interface between personal glucose monitoring devices and a health management database to assist in the review, analysis, and evaluation of blood glucose test results for home and professional healthcare settings
